{"tid":2378761,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲網紅孫藝軒「腦溢血猝死」！　為出名長期暴飲暴食…震驚全網","createTime":"2021-01-24T17:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T05:28:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a22328d1a2090e70ae6527b66790d9865ab104","tid":2378761,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"隨著科技發展進步，許多素人會透過社群、直播平台展現個人長才，闖出名聲成為「網紅」，為了維持熱度，背後總是付出不少心血。近日有大陸網友爆料，一名年僅19歲的吃播網紅孫藝軒，突然腦溢血猝死，並指他經常暴飲暴食，消息震驚網友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5418/5418114.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5418%2F5418114.jpg&h=b6336e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吃播網紅孫藝軒風格搞笑，受粉絲喜愛。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n據《時間視頻》報導，有大陸網友22日爆料，一位名叫孫藝軒的網紅因腦溢血去世，年僅19歲。據悉，孫藝軒在影音平台上擁有近50萬個粉絲，經常分享日常飲食，風格浮誇、搞笑，備受喜愛。而他為了增加個人知名度，時常暴飲暴食，長期攝取高熱量、高油脂的食物，憾事發生令網友相當震驚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5418/5418117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5418%2F5418117.jpg&h=38bc6981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友爆料孫藝軒過世。（圖／翻攝自微博／時間視頻）<br />\n<br />\n另外，網友還發現，孫藝軒過去每天都會上傳新影片，但至今已經7天沒有更新，曾和他合作的其它網紅，都紛紛發文悼念，他的朋友也貼出兩人合影，表示對好友死訊不敢相信，寫下：「還沒見最後一面，還有好多話沒有說，好好的一個人怎麼突然&hellip;。」語氣相當難過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5418/5418116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5418%2F5418116.jpg&h=f416691f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲合作過的網紅、朋友發文。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n網友得知消息大感震驚，留言「好可惜，超級喜歡他」、「不敢相信，經常看到他影片，怎麼這麼突然就去世了」、「莫名的心酸」、「以後世界少了一份快樂」、「2021年除了暴富多一個願望，就是健康」、「真希望誰出來闢個謠」、「這麼多天吃了這麼多瓜，唯一讓人難過的是你」。"},{"pid":"24d9a409721e1177dae0ed688539424d175ea315","tid":2378761,"uid":388276,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T17:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1XzHtZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1XzHtZ.gif&h=1a1a59ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b92b0a50808b581ea91ad9729f9cf22848740573","tid":2378761,"uid":199736,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T17:58:45.000Z","msg":"腦溢血即係中風？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58826c399aee5e7c1b537a653957c48c0612777","tid":2378761,"uid":263223,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"暴飲暴食未必死，但暴飲暴食支那元素表就死9緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a7fef38ec8d51055a17f6b4534759d3fca5be7","tid":2378761,"uid":53666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:01:21.000Z","msg":"個樣39"},{"pid":"5e7b7d706cae1cda757a4d3f0bfba1292c699357","tid":2378761,"uid":183844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"24d9a409721e1177dae0ed688539424d175ea315","tid":2378761,"uid":388276,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T17:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1XzHtZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1XzHtZ.gif&h=1a1a59ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:05:48.000Z","msg":"支那人太多<br />\n想紅嘅一朝發達全香港人各10隻手指加埋都數唔哂<br />\n你唔識係正常㗎"},{"pid":"6031714b7eb17582f92afc0c9ead24132c5d3ec2","tid":2378761,"uid":7854,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/3ofSBdCOi8tYqKmv4s/giphy-downsized-large.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ofSBdCOi8tYqKmv4s%2Fgiphy-downsized-large.gif&h=aac3ac22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b18878f24df441e7104aa23031b039c97c5e42f7","tid":2378761,"uid":213529,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />來生再做中國人"},{"pid":"5e0d14f2fa6c84e8ab9a11f9a2847e85749b8a25","tid":2378761,"uid":16567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim